HEADWORD: Immediateness
<hw>Im*me"di*ate*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or relations
of being immediate in manner, place, or time; exemption from second or
interventing causes.</def> <rj><au>Bp. Hall.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

